snippet.title: Diana is preparing a School Project | Helping Each Other
snippet.description:
Diana needs to prepare a school project. But someone is constantly distracting her. Diana helps Oliver, Roma, mom and dad and doesn't have time to finish her school assignment. In the evening the whole family gathered to help Diana. Useful video for children about how important it is to help each other!
Thanks for watching!
